2:14:20.000Z","msg":"畀左幾多百億畀國泰？"},{"pid":"74d9b46c62e6f25288694c86410449389427ffde","tid":2510742,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"加税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開銷售税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陸路離境税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燃油税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車牌牌費加一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣樓加一倍税<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n股票印花稅再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f0013c0517990983efef3a232025eced990248","tid":2510742,"uid":13545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"說好的有國安法就經濟繁榮呢？"},{"pid":"33c0a30c33e7b3e1211196ddb723542c0e55013f","tid":2510742,"uid":64165,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7797276c0cbf0d097963a0334936040a047369fe","tid":2510742,"uid":24788,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"好撚癲<br />\n前幾日重建警察宿舍要20億<br />\n警察財政預算258億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但全港薪俸稅收入得600幾億"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"香港人交稅一半養狗<br />\n另一半養蝗"},{"pid":"9e9aa9b5b040038f5b88e6e1eaae53e80b5fbca2","tid":2510742,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"攬炒成功！"},{"pid":"1100fa2aa7fc0a3cb499cb4bdc6abab315996e0f","tid":2510742,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5dfe0f21980fdf389033bfce5dd2aa93af835f47","tid":2510742,"uid":21896,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"增加印花稅喇，樓市咁暢旺，幾多稅都阻止唔到香港人買樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"境外加一倍咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />